## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **abiraterone Zytiga 2011** = first FDA CYP17A1 inhibitor — mCRPC post-doce + 2017 mHSPC LATITUDE 1L. 17α-hydroxylase + 17,20-lyase dual block. quantum-VQE 의 CYP17A1 pocket scaffold 가 직접 fit.
2. **enzalutamide Xtandi 2012** = first FDA next-gen AR antagonist — mCRPC + 2018 nmCRPC PROSPER + 2019 mHSPC ARCHES expansion. AR LBD + nuclear translocation + DNA binding triple block. quantum-VQE 의 AR LBD pocket leverage.
3. **177Lu-PSMA-617 Pluvicto 2022** = first FDA PSMA radioligand mCRPC. β-emitter 6.7 MeV + 6.7 day half-life. theranostic paradigm shift. quantum-VQE 의 PSMA pocket + DOTA chelator scaffold.
4. **olaparib + rucaparib + niraparib + talazoparib 2020-2023** = PARP inhibitor mPC paradigm shift. BRCA-mutated + HRD synthetic lethality. abiraterone combo (PROpel) + enzalutamide combo (TALAPRO-2) + niraparib+abi (Akeega) 1L 확장.
5. **bavdegalutamide ARV-110 + ARV-766** = first PROTAC clinical AR + AR-V7. AR-V7 splice variant 가 enzalutamide resistance driver. quantum-VQE 의 PROTAC ternary leverage.
6. **darolutamide Nubeqa 2019 + 2024 ARANOTE mHSPC** = third-gen AR — non-permeable BBB → CNS adverse 감소. apalutamide + enzalutamide vs darolutamide CNS profile distinct.
7. **sipuleucel-T Provenge 2010** = first FDA cell therapy mPC. autologous DC + PAP-GM-CSF fusion. CAR-T 이전 cell therapy era. quantum-VQE 의 PAP-MHC class I 결합 modeling 한정.
8. **radium-223 Xofigo 2013** = first α-emitter bone metastasis CRPC. Ca-mimetic bone-seeker. 만성 bone metastasis SRE 감소 + OS extension.
9. **relugolix Orgovyx 2020** = first FDA oral LHRH antagonist. degarelix injection 후 oral compliance 향상. cardiovascular safety (HERO trial) — leuprolide 대비 cardiac event 54% 감소.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, prostate cancer specific 임상 의미 한정.

